clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日扮廢唔夠打 之後又秒鳩人</blockquote><br />\n一兩次都算 仲要獲獲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1237954c6cd6532e02b911429eb33c575276c6e0","tid":328931,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"好好睇喎"},{"pid":"ecc2c2787ba04ac63b6da6c214b1af4af44572a5","tid":328931,"uid":6521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"每一個罪既回憶堅係世界級<br />\n打鬥就睇太陽屈機都幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe77415d7a41ee3194d3c8670479c65956b9bdf","tid":328931,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>七影帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日扮廢唔夠打 之後又秒鳩人</blockquote><br />\n一兩次都算 仲要獲獲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主係咪打錯標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(其實七大罪&quot;外傳&quot;好好睇)<br />\n<br />\n當初睇頭果兩話見到個騎士丟枝長槍去團長到然後團長丟返過去，果下真係型，吸引落去睇<br />\n<br />\n跟住講到去十戒、鬥級、經常性假便當，我就覺得我睇頭嗰100話比人呃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你同聖騎士打到半生半死，去到十戒騎士無撚左影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成班影帝成日扮重傷<br />\n<br />\n不過套野既人物外傳就ok，有感人位"},{"pid":"45f13dd228534efe26b1f01289b7697641873ba3","tid":328931,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"呢套野既缺點係戰力失衡，吹到敵人好撚勁<br />\n之後自己友就突然有新掛or一路做緊戲<br />\n戰鬥力大提升，但只限主角群<br />\n你睇下一開始出場嗰啲，雷帝，亨德里克森<br />\n去到後期變戰五渣"},{"pid":"c25164afc16545f5816164e588af4663f68a2209","tid":328931,"uid":25794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"可以屌百幾次處女伊莉莎白"},{"pid":"f1bf3abb3b17a97215a497871a0ef86d29af1339","tid":328931,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:26